data.name: label6.Text
data.value: There are three modes of operation: single picture, multi-picture and slide show. In the single picture mode, when the user selects a picture from the listbox, the picture is displayed in a picturebox. In the slide show mode, all the pictures are displayed in a picturebox in sequence in 0.10 sec interval. In the multi-picture mode, when a user selects a number of pictures from the listbox, all the selected pictures are displayed in a number of picture boxes equal to the number of the selected pictures
